if \- Simple shell conditional.
.SH EXAMPLES
.PP
Echo a different thing depending on a command\[aq]s success:
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
{{command}}\ &&\ echo\ "success"\ ||\ echo\ "failure"
\f[]
.fi
.PP
Full if syntax:
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
if\ {{condition}};\ then\ echo\ "true";\ else\ echo\ "false";\ fi
\f[]
.fi
